<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>하이볼리 사용 정보 저장하기</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>제공할 하이볼을 선택해주세요</h1>
    <form action="/qr/confirm/update" method="post">
        <div>
            <p>가게 이름: <span id="restaurant_name"><%= restaurant_name %></span></p>
            <p>
                제공가능한 하이볼 리스트:
                <select id="highball_select" name="selectHighball">
                    <% for (let i = 0; i < highballArray.length; i++) { %>
                        <option value="<%= highballArray[i] %>"><%= highballArray[i] %></option>
                    <% } %>
                </select>
            </p>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= id %>">
        <input type="hidden" name="restaurant_id" value="<%= restaurant_id %>">
        <input type="hidden" name="restaurant_name" value="<%= restaurant_name %>">
        <button type="submit">저장하기</button> <!-- Add a submit button -->
    </form>
</body>
</html>
